{{Quote|Xharnoh plants are most often found along rivers and streams that flow out from the bottom of a waterfall. Walk along the river until you find some.|[[Lieutenant/Legends|Lieutenant]] [[Karenna Dunnels|Dunnels]], to a spacer|<ref name="SWG:HLDwitmNB">{{SWGcite|exp=NGE|type=class|Legacy|Help Lt. Dunnels with ingredients to make Neural Boosters|Naboo}}</ref>}}
The '''xharnoh plant''' was a plant that was found on [[Naboo/Legends|Naboo]]. It grew on the sides of Naboo's various rivers and lakes. Their roots were used to make neural enhancers. In [[1 ABY/Legends|1 ABY]] [[Lieutenant/Legends|Lieutenant]] [[Karenna Dunnels]] of the [[Royal Naboo Security Forces/Legends|Royal Naboo Security Forces]] hired a [[Spacer/Legends|spacer]] to collect a number of roots to make [[Stimulant/Legends|neural boosters]] for the security force,<ref name="SWG:HLDwitmNB" /> prior to the [[raid on the Mummer bunker]].<ref name="SWG:BTttT">{{SWGcite|exp=NGE|type=class|Legacy|Bring Terror to the Terrorists|Naboo}}</ref>

==Behind the scenes==
Xharnoh plants appeared in the [[2003]] [[Star Wars video games|video game]] ''[[Star Wars Galaxies]]'', a [[Wikipedia:Massively multiplayer online role-playing game|massively multiplayer online roleplaying game]] developed by [[Sony]] Online Entertainment and published by [[LucasArts]],<ref name="SWG:HLDwitmNB" /> prior to its closure on [[December 15]], [[2011]].<ref name="Shutdown">{{SonyCite|url=playerinfo|text=IMPORTANT INFORMATION ABOUT ''STAR WARS'' GALAXIES™}}</ref> Xharnoh plants were added to the game as part of the "[[W:c:swg:Legacy Quest|Legacy Quest]]" with the release of the "[[W:c:swg:Publish 25 Notes for November 15, 2005|Publish 25]]," a.k.a. the "[[W:c:swg:New Game Enhancements|New Game Enhancements]]," on [[November 15]], [[2005]].<ref name="SonyCite-Publish Archive 2005">{{SonyCite|url=players/content.vm?id=64886&resource=publish|text=Publish Archive 2005}}</ref> Xharnoh plants used the same model than the [[raventhorn plant]]s found on [[Yavin 4/Legends|Yavin 4]].<ref name="SWG">{{GalaxiesAED}}</ref>

